addBoxes

  • addBoxes(html: string, containerSelector: string, nodeSelector: string, boxTag: string): string

  • Transforms a HTML structure wrapping sections of a flat lists node's into boxes.

    Parameters

    • html: string
    • containerSelector: string

      jQuery selector for the container node(s) of the list

    • nodeSelector: string

      jQuery selector for the nodes to start a box at

    • boxTag: string

      full html tag snipped including attributes to wrap boxes in - e.g. <div class="movie"></div>
